snippet.textDisplay: "chehra ek pal yakeein, chehra ek pal gumaan" , no matter how much you think about it, it keeps getting deeper and deeper. I was in love with the song when legendary Nusrat sahab sang it, but this one has done full justice to one of the greatest singers of the subcontinent, and to one of the most prolific poets. All those who bring india and Pakistan into it, all those who want to own this creation , all those who think religion as a response to this, have a long way to go still. thank you for uploading this .
